{"tid":559233,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網紅T妹懷男娃竟說「父不詳」　徴男士埋單","createTime":"2018-02-13T04:05:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-13T05:38:40.000Z","uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"22e4eb52da7a7a86223a468991e1a6d1708911db","tid":559233,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T04:05:11.000Z","msg":"網紅T妹（Tiffany　Chen）近來較少曝光，但行事向來天不怕地不怕的她，最近竟然被爆懷孕了！昨她坦承已懷孕17周，肚中娃娃是男孩，不過一被問到孩子的爸是誰？她竟答：「這個是個人隱私，我想保密，你可以說是父不詳。」還笑說徵求一位男士幫她認養小孩。<br />\n<br />\nT妹說到自己懷孕這件事有點害羞，卻又期待兒子到來，「懷孕的不舒服我都嘗到了，也變得比較多愁善感，例如要是有網友罵我，過去我會置之不理，現在卻會難過很久」。她說預產期約莫在7月，屆時媽媽會從澳洲回來幫她坐月子。<br />\nT妹當媽後，不斷去搜尋跟懷孕有關的資訊：「其實台灣懷孕率跟全球一樣，但生產率一年才20萬 （比全球低），墮胎就高達50萬人（比全球高），為何墮胎率這麼高？很多是因為男方後來不負責，女生選擇殺生自私拿掉，很多都16周以上，而且女性不夠獨立，又堅持要男生娶，如果這麼堅持應該要結婚才受孕，不然對生命是很不負責。」<br />\nT妹聊到近況，說到她去按摩時，店家要她簽切結書，因怕孕婦流產會提告，「我在澳洲就開美容Spa店，孕婦是可以按摩，只要不在腰背的地方敲打或壓迫肚子，其實都可以」。她還笑說徵求一位男士幫她認養小孩，順便談戀愛，完全不怕世俗眼光。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.entertainment.appledaily.com/realtime/20180213/1297459\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Frealtime%2F20180213%2F1297459&d=hAob8PXt6f46nKZTGsFS6QdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=f563ab5e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Frealtime%2F20180213%2F1297459&h=f4da9297\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.entertainment.appledaily.com/realtime/20180213/1297459</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180213/640_27ced2e3779236ec7605d9d73affe461.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180213%2F640_27ced2e3779236ec7605d9d73affe461.jpg&h=a3759eb7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180213/640_9b707863c85c24a1b4da5d0ad2f99e62.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180213%2F640_9b707863c85c24a1b4da5d0ad2f99e62.jpg&h=ecc5371e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180213/640_086d44473375cbc6d495817a2b0a0189.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180213%2F640_086d44473375cbc6d495817a2b0a0189.jpg&h=583773b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 俾錢屌你唔緊要，埋單不了"},{"pid":"960d9df23bcd5a1bfdcd6ea5ce8a456064accca7","tid":559233,"uid":133529,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T04:12:27.000Z","msg":"雖然你班毒撚埋單預咗，但問題係，買大送細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ea7902e10ac484029c6f56d72938dddd5f969c4","tid":559233,"uid":38668,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T04:14:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可以玩父不詳 當晚一定好似H漫情節咁玩法"},{"pid":"1811e49ae5f05aafa82b37f7f2c66ba02fa65096","tid":559233,"uid":23087,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T04:14:53.000Z","msg":"who the fuck is she?"},{"pid":"bfa076fb18f11df31fe81c0164fbdf0190b65929","tid":559233,"uid":7638,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T04:22:04.000Z","msg":"想保密，定係太多個唔知邊個先係呀"},{"pid":"79c2a9a3fec83c366302e826471db23ad794ced3","tid":559233,"uid":7439,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T04:34:35.000Z","msg":"徴男士埋單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.makeagif.com/media/1-22-2018/rtrO3L.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.makeagif.com%2Fmedia%2F1-22-2018%2FrtrO3L.gif&h=8aa27647&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2018-02-13<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">(今晚)20:00</span></strong></span> - 天津權健 (中國) vs 傑志 @天津奧林匹克體育中心體育場 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">20